snippet.title: Sabertooth vs Raptor: Who Would Win?
snippet.description:
This is the first of a new series I'm calling "The Anachro-Lab", an animated series depicting fights between species who normally were separated by millions of years. This pilot episode took two years to produce! The next episode is already underway and will hopefully take a bit less time to create. 

Credits:

Writing, editing, production, directing: Patrick Lacey

3D Animation: WobblyWorks

3D Modeling: Kuzim

Storyboarding: Trinity

Sound designer & foley: Manni Simon

Sound effects editor: Dony Bullen

Music:

Loop Hero - Entropic Rhapsody by blinch: https://youtu.be/43mlgU-HCRk?si=ELUe2je1p_dIEXJC

Eyewitness theme remix by fishstix (Original theme by Guy Michaelmore): https://youtu.be/x7JN4hbQtNQ?si=U2RostcF2t_Ktkdm
